(23, 18, 'CGST Rule 1', 'Rule 1 : Short title, Extent and Commencement', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">CHAPTER\r\nI - PRELIMINARY<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:178.05pt\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:1.65pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-indent:-14.05pt;line-height:\r\n107%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:13.6pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;