(25, 18, 'CGST Rule 3', 'Rule 3 : Intimation for composition levy', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">CHAPTER\r\nII - COMPOSITION [LEVY]1<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:13.2pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Intimation\r\nfor composition levy.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:13.2pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><br></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1) Any person who has been granted\r\nregistration on<b> </b>a provisional basis under clause (b) of sub-rule (1) of\r\nrule 24 and who opts to pay tax under section 10, shall electronically file an\r\nintimation in <b>FORM GST CMP-01</b>, duly signed or verified through\r\nelectronic verification code, on the common portal, either directly or through\r\na Facilitation Centre notified by the Commissioner, prior to the appointed day,\r\nbut not later than thirty days after the said day, or such further period as\r\nmay be extended by the Commissioner in this behalf:<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:8.85pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:28.45pt;line-height:112%\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that where the\r\nintimation in <b>FORM GST CMP-01</b> is filed after the appointed day, the\r\nregistered person shall not collect any tax from the appointed day but shall\r\nissue bill of supply for supplies made after the said day.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:112%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:8.7pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:.1pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:32.3pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Any person who applies for registration\r\nunder sub-rule (1) of rule 8 may give an option to pay tax under section 10 in\r\nPart B of <b>FORM GST REG-01</b>, which shall be considered as an intimation to\r\npay tax under the said section.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:8.3pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;\r\