 serif; color: windowtext;\">Application\r\nfor registration.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:16.7pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><br></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)Every person, other than a non-resident\r\ntaxable<b> </b>person, a person required to deduct tax at source under section\r\n51, a person required to collect tax at source under section 52 and a person\r\nsupplying online information and database access or retrieval services from a\r\nplace outside India to a non-taxable online recipient referred to in section 14\r\nof the Integrated Goods and Services Tax Act, 2017 (13 of 2017) who is liable\r\nto be registered under sub-section (1) of section 25 and every person seeking\r\nregistration under sub-section (3) of section 25 (hereafter in this<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.8pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial\">Chapter referred to as ?the\r\napplicant?) shall, before applying for registration, declare </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">his\r\nPermanent Account Number, mobile number, e-mail address, State or Union\r\nterritory in <b>Part A</b> of <b>FORM GST REG-01</b> on the common portal,\r\neither directly or through a Facilitation Centre notified by the Commissioner:<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.3pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:21.85pt;line-height:110%\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[<s>Provided that a person\r\nhaving a unit(s) in a Special Economic Zone or being</s> <s>a Special Economic\r\nZone developer shall make a separate application for registration as a business\r\nvertical distinct from his other units located outside the Special Economic\r\nZone:]</s></span><s><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:110%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">8</span></sup></s><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.0pt;line-height:110%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:28.45pt;line-height:103%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided\r\n[<s>further</s>]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:103%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">9</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:103%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> that every person being an Input Service\r\nDistributor shall make a separate application for registration as such Input\r\nService Distributor.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:103%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:17.7pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:113%;\r\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:35.9pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(a) The Permanent Account Number shall be\r\nvalidated online by the common portal from the database maintained by the\r\nCentral Board of Direct Taxes.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-indent:14.25pt;line-height:\r\n113%;mso-list:l1 level3 lfo2;tab-stops:71.9pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The mobile number declared under sub-rule\r\n(1) shall be verified through a one-time password sent to the said mobile\r\nnumber; and<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.4pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:12.1pt;line-height:113%;\r\nmso-list:l1 level2 lfo2;tab-stops:71.9pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(c)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The e-mail address declared under sub-rule\r\n(1) shall be verified through a separate one-time password sent to the said\r\ne-mail address.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:35.9pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">On\r\nsuccessful verification of the Permanent Account Number, mobile number and\r\ne-mail address, a temporary reference number shall be generated and\r\ncommunicated to the applicant on the said mobile number and e-mail address.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:35.9pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Using\r\nthe reference number generated under sub-rule (3), the applicant shall\r\nelectronically submit an application in <b>Part B</b> of <b>FORM GST REG-01</b>,\r\nduly signed or verified through electronic verification code, along with the\r\ndocuments specified in the said Form at the common portal, either directly or\r\nthrough a Facilitation Centre notified by the Commissioner.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.6pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideo