;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.05pt;text-indent:-36.05pt;mso-list:\r\nl0 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:36.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">(a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">such person has more than one business vertical as defined\r\nin clause (18) of section 2;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.55pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:97%;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:38.6pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:97%;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">(b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:97%;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">the business vertical of a taxable\r\nperson shall not be granted registration to pay tax under section 10 if any one\r\nof the other business verticals of the same person is paying tax under section\r\n9;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.6pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:3.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:2.45pt;line-height:97%;\r\nmso-list:l0 level2 lfo4;tab-stops:36.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:97%;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">(c)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:97%;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">all separately registered business\r\nverticals of such person shall pay tax under the Act on supply of goods or\r\nservices or both made to another registered business vertical of such person\r\nand issue a tax invoice for such supply.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.65pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:98%\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:\r\n98%;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Explanation.- For the purposes\r\nof clause (b), it is hereby clarified that where any business vertical of a\r\nregistered person that has been granted a separate registration becomes\r\nineligible to pay tax under section 10, all other business verticals of the\r\nsaid person shall become ineligible to pay tax under the said section.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:98%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.65pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:97%;\r\nmso-list:l2 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:36.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:97%;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">(1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:97%;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">A registered person eligible to\r\nobtain separate registration for business verticals may submit a separate\r\napplication in FORM GST REG-01 in respect of each such vertical.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.05pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iii_registration_rule_11', 1, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:05:18', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:05:18'),
(35, 18, 'CGST Rule 12', 'Rule 12 : Grant of registration to persons required to deduct tax at source or to collect tax at source', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">CHAPTER III- REGISTRATION<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -14.05pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:111%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">12.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -14.05pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 0.875rem;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Grant\r\nof registration to persons required to deduct tax at source or to collect tax\r\nat</span></b></a><b style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -14.05pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:111%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> </span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -14.05pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 0.875rem;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">source.</span></b></a><b style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -14.05pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:111%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -14.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(1)Any person required to deduct tax in\r\naccordance with the provisions of<b> </b>section 51 or a person required to\r\ncollect tax at source in accordance with the provisionsofsection 52 shall\r\nelectronically submit an application, duly signed or verified through\r\nelectronic verification code, in <b>FORM GST REG-07</b> for the grant of\r\nregistration through the common portal, either directly or through a\r\nFacilitation Centre notified by the Commissioner.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:112%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[(1A) A person applying for registration to\r\n[deduct or]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:112%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">15</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">collect tax in accordance with the\r\nprovisions of [section 51, or, as the case may be,]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">16</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">section\r\n52, in a State or Union territory where he does not have a physical presence,\r\nshall mention the name of the State or Union territory in <b>PART A</b> of the\r\napplication in <b>FORM GST REG-07</b> and mention the name of the State or\r\nUnion territory in <b>PART B</b> thereof in which the principal place of\r\nbusiness is located which may be different from the State or Union territory\r\nmentioned in <b>PART A</b>.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">17</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:112%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:19.3pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:.1pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:35.15pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The proper officer may grant registration\r\nafter due verification and issue a certificate of registration in <b>FORM GST\r\nREG-06</b> within a period of three working days from the date ofsubmission of\r\nthe application.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:12.2pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:32.75pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Where,\r\nupon anenquiry or pursuant to any other proceeding under the Act, the proper\r\nofficer is satisfied that a person to whom a certificate of registration in <b>FORM</b>\r\n<b>GST REG-06 </b>has been issued is no longer liable to deduct tax at source\r\nunder section<b> </b>51 or collect tax at source under section 52, the said\r\nofficer may cancel the registration issued under sub-rule (2) and such\r\ncancellation shall be communicated to the said person electronically in <b>FORM\r\nGST REG-08:</b><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.7pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-indent:28.45pt;line-height:\r\n112%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided\r\nthat the proper officer shall follow the procedure as provided in rule 22 for\r\nthe cancellation of registration.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:112%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.95pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iii_registration_rule_12', 1, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:05:45', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:05:45');
