(36, 18, 'CGST Rule 13', 'Rule 13 : Grant of registration to non-resident taxable person', '<div class=\"WordSection1\">\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;CHAPTER III -REGISTRATION<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:10.95pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:22.45pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">13.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Grant\r\nof registration to non-resident taxable person.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:22.45pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)A\r\nnon-resident taxable<b> </b>person shall electronically submit an application,\r\nalong with a self-attested copy of his valid passport, for registration, duly\r\nsigned or verified through electronic verification code, in <b>FORM GST REG-09</b>,\r\nat least five days prior to the commencement of business at the common portal\r\neither directly or through a Facilitation Centre notified by the Commissioner:<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.75pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 28.45pt;\">Provided\r\nthat in the case of a business entity incorporated or estab