ted\r\nvide Notf no. 74/2018-CT dt. 31.12.2018<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt;\">identification\r\nnumber or unique number on the basis of which the entity is identified by the\r\nGovernment of that country or its Permanent Account Number, if available.</span></p></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.6pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.1pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.1pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">A\r\nperson applying for registration as a non-resident taxable person shall be\r\ngiven a temporary referencenumber by the common portal for makingan advance\r\ndeposit of tax in accordance with the provisions of section 27 and the\r\nacknowledgement under sub-rule (5) of rule 8 shall be issued electronically only\r\nafter the said deposit in his electronic cash ledger.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0.1pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0.1pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">The provisions of rule 9 and rule 10\r\nrelating to the verification and the grant of registration shall, <i>mutatis\r\nmutandis,</i> apply to an application submittedunder this rule.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">The application for registration\r\nmade by a non-resident taxable person shall be [duly signed or verified through\r\nelectronic verification code]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">18</span></sup><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">by his authorised signatory who shall be a\r\nperson resident in India having a valid Permanent Account Number.</span></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iii_registration_rule_13', 1, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:06:14', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:06:14'),
(37, 18, 'CGST Rule 14', 'Rule 14 : Grant of registration to a person supplying online information and database access or retrieval services from a place outside India to a non-taxable online recipient', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;CHAPTER III -REGISTRATION<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:10.95pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:20.05pt;text-indent:-20.05pt;mso-list:\r\nl0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:20.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">14.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stret