s or\r\nretrieval services from a place outside India to a non-taxable online recipient\r\nshall electronically submit an application for registration, duly signed or\r\nverified through electronic verification code, in<b>FORM GST REG-10</b>, at the\r\ncommon portal, either directly or through a Facilitation Centre notified by the\r\nCommissioner.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.65pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:111%;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:30.95pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:111%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:111%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The\r\napplicant referred to in sub-rule (1) shall be granted registration, in<b>FORM\r\nGST</b> <b>REG-06, </b>subject to such conditions and restrictions and by such\r\nofficer as may be<b> </b>notified by the Central Government on the\r\nrecommendations of the Council.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-b