(39, 18, 'CGST Rule 16', 'Rule 16 : Suo moto registration', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;CHAPTER III -REGISTRATION<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:11.0pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></sup></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:20.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">16.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></i></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Suomoto </span></i></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">registration.</span></b></a><b><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></i></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:20.05pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)\r\nWhere, pursuant to any survey, enquiry, inspection, search<b><i> </i></b>or any\r\nother proceedings under the Act, the proper officer finds that a person liable\r\nto registration under the Act has failed to apply for such registration, such\r\nofficer may register the said person on a temporary basis and issue an order in\r\n<b>FORM GST REG-12</b>.<b><i><o:p></o:p></i></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></spa