\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Every person to whom a\r\ntemporary registration has been granted under sub-rule<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.35pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:.1pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo2;tab-stops:31.55pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">shall, within a period of ninetydays from\r\nthe date of the grant of such registration, submit an application for\r\nregistration in the form and manner provided in rule 8 or rule 12:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:28.45pt;line-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that where the said person has\r\nfiled an appeal against the grant of temporary registration, in such case, the\r\napplication for registration shall be submitted within a period of thirty days\r\nfrom the date of the issuance of the order upholding the liability to\r\nregistration by the Appellate Authority.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3;\r\ntab-stops:35.9pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The\r\nprovisions of rule 9 and rule 10 relating to verification and the issue of the\r\ncertificate of registration shall, <i>mutatis mutandis,</i> apply to an\r\napplication submitted under sub-rule (3).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:.1pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:35.9pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The Goods and Services Tax Identification\r\nNumber assigned, pursuant to the verification under sub-rule (4), shall be\r\neffective from the date of the order granting registration under sub-rule (1).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.65pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iii_registration_rule_16', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:10:15', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:10:15'),
(40, 18, 'CGST Rule 17', 'Rule 17 : Assignment of Unique Identity Number to certain special entities', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;CHAPTER III- REGISTRATION<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:11.0pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:10.65pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.1pt;line-height:112%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">17.</span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Assignment\r\nof Unique Identity Number to certain special entities.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.1pt;line-height:112%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><br></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)\r\nEvery person<b> </b>required to be granted a Unique Identity Number in\r\naccordance with the provisions of sub-section (9) of section 25 may submit an\r\napplication electronically in <b>FORM GST</b> <b>REG-13</b>, duly signed or\r\nverified through electronic verification code, in the manner<b> </b>specified\r\nin rule 8 at the common portal, either directly or through a Facilitation\r\nCentre notified by the Commissioner.<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.65pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:123%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:123%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[(1A)\r\nThe Unique Identity Number granted under sub-rule (1) to a person under clause\r\n(a) of sub-section (9) of section 25 shall be applicable to the territory of\r\nIndia.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:123%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">19</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:123%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:1.35pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:32.05pt;text-indent:-17.9pt;mso-list:\r\nl0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:32.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The proper officer may, upon\r\nsubmission of an application in <b>FORM GST REG-</b><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.7pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">13 </span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">or after filling up the\r\nsaid formor after receiving a recommendation from the<b> </b>Ministry of\r\nExternal Affairs, Government of India</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">20</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">, assign a Unique Identity Number to the said\r\nperson and issue a certificate in <b>FORM GST REG-06</b> within a period of\r\nthree working days from the date of the submission of the application</span><br></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iii_registration_rule_17', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:11:12', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:11:12');
