(45, 18, 'CGST Rule 21A', 'Rule 21A : Suspension of registration', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;CHAPTER III- REGISTRATION<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:9.0pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-14.1pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[<b>Rule 21A Suspension of registration.-</b></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-14.1pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1) Where a registered person has applied\r\nfor cancellation of registration under rule 20, the registration shall be\r\ndeemed to be suspended from the date of submission of the application or the\r\ndate from which the cancellation is sought, whichever is later, pending the\r\ncompletion of proceedings for cancellation of registration under rule 22.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:11.75pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:31.95pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Where\r\nthe proper officer has reasons to believe that the registration of a person is\r\nliable to be cancelled under section 29 or under rule 21, he may, after\r\naffording the said person a reasonable opportunity of being heard, suspend the\r\nregistration of such person with effect from a date to be determined by him,\r\npending the completion of the proceedings for cancellation of registration\r\nunder rule 22.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:.1pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:32.3pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">A registered person, whose registration has\r\nbeen suspended under sub-rule (1) or sub-rule (2), shall not make any taxable\r\nsupply during the period of suspension and shall not be required to furnish any\r\nreturn under section 39.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:1.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:line\r\n id=\"Shape_x0020_16\" o:spid=\"_x0000_s1026\" style=\'position:absolute;z-index:-251732480;\r\n visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square;mso-wrap-distance-left:9pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-top:0;mso-wrap-distance-right:9pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-bottom:0;mso-position-horizontal:absolute;\r\n mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;mso-position-vertical:absolute;\r\n mso-position-vertical