isto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial\">taxable\r\nsupply? shall mean that the registered person shall not issue a tax invoice\r\nand, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">accordingly,\r\nnot charge tax on supplies made by him during the period of suspension.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">26</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.8pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:117%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:31.45pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:117%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:117%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The\r\nsuspension of registration under sub-rule (1) or sub-rule (2) shall be deemed\r\nto be revoked upon completion of the proceedings by the proper officer under\r\nrule 22 and such revocation shall be effective from the date on which the\r\nsuspension had come into effect.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:117%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">27</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:117%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.6pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">[(5) Where any order having\r\nthe effect of revocation of suspension of registration has been passed, the\r\nprovisions of clause (a) of sub-section (3) of section 31 and section 40 in\r\nrespect of the supplies made during the period of suspension and the procedure\r\nspecified therein shall apply.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">28</span></sup><br></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iii_registration_rule_21a', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:13:38', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:13:38'),
(46, 18, 'CGST Rule 22', 'Rule 22 : Cancellation of registration', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;CHAPTER III- REGISTRATION<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:9.0pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.1pt;line-height:112%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">22.</span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Cancellation\r\nof registration.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.1pt;line-height:112%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><br></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1) Where the proper officer has reasons to\r\nbelieve that<b> </b>the registration of a person is liable to be cancelled\r\nunder section 29, he shall issue a notice to suchperson in <b>FORM GST REG-17</b>,requiring\r\nhim to show cause, within a period of seven working days from the date of the\r\nservice of such notice, as to why his registration shall not be cancelled.<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.75pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:\r\n112%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:33.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The reply to the show cause notice issued\r\nunder sub-rule (1) shall be furnished in<b>FORM REG–18</b> within the period\r\nspecified in the said sub-rule.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.7pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:112%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(3)Where a person who has submitted an\r\napplication for cancellation of his registration is no longer liable to be\r\nregistered or his registration is liable to be cancelled, the proper officer\r\nshall issue an order in <b>FORM GST REG-19</b>, within a period of thirty days\r\nfrom the date of application submitted under [<s>sub-rule (1) of</s>]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">29</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> rule\r\n20 or, as the case may be, the date of the reply to the show cause issued under\r\nsub-rule (1), cancel the registration, with effect from a date to be determined\r\nby him and notify the taxable person, directing him to pay arrears of any tax,\r\ninterest or penalty including the amount liable to be paid under sub-section\r\n(5) of section 29.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:112%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.95pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:\r\n112%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:31.45pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Where the reply furnished under sub-rule (2)\r\nis found to be satisfactory, the proper officer shall drop the proceedings and\r\npass an order in<b>FORM GST REG</b> <b>–20:</b><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[Provided that where the person instead of\r\nreplying to the notice served under sub-rule</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.35pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:112%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3;\r\ntab-stops:33.15pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">for\r\ncontravention of the provisions contained in clause (b) or clause (c) of\r\nsub-section (2) of section 29, furnishes all the pending returns and makes full\r\npayment of the tax dues along with applicable interest and late fee, the proper\r\nofficer shall drop the proceedings and pass an order in <b>FORM GST-REG 20]</b></span><b><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">30</span></sup></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:5.55pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:112%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4;\r\ntab-stops:35.9pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The\r\nprovisions of sub-rule (3) shall, <i>mutatis mutandis,</i> apply to the legal\r\nheirs of a deceased proprietor, as if the application had been submitted by the\r\nproprietor himself.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iii_registration_rule_22', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:14:15', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:14:15'),
(47, 18, 'CGST Rule 23', 'Rule 23 : Revocation of cancellation of registration', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;CHAPTER III- REGISTRATION<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:9.0pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:19.8pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">23.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Revocation of cancellation of registration.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:19.8pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)Aregisteredperson,\r\nwhose registration<b> </b>is cancelled by the proper officer on his own motion,\r\nmay submit an application for revocation of cancellation of registration, in <b>FORM\r\nGST REG-21</b>, to such proper officer, within a period of thirty days from the\r\ndate of the service of the order of cancellation of registration at the common\r\nportal, either directly or through a Facilitation Centre notified by the\r\nCommissioner:<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.75pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:28.45pt;line-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that no application\r\nfor revocation shall be filed, if the registration has been cancelled for the\r\nfailure of the registered person to furnish returns, unless such returns are\r\nfurnished and any amount due as tax, in terms of such returns, has been paid\r\nalong with any amount payable towards interest, penalty and late fee in respect\r\nof the said returns:</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.65pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:28.45pt;line-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[Provided further that all returns due for\r\nthe period from the date of the order of cancellation of registration till the\r\ndate of the order of revocation of cancellation of registration shall be\r\nfurnished by the said person within a period of thirty days from the date of\r\norder of revocation of cancellation of registration:</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.35pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:31.45pt;line-height:117%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n117%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided also that where the registration\r\nhas been cancelled with retrospective effect, the registered person shall\r\nfurnish all returns relating to period from the effective date of cancellation\r\nof registration till the date of order of revocation of cancellation of\r\nregistration within a period of thirty days from the date of order of\r\nrevocation of cancellation of registration]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:117%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">31</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:117%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.55pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:31.7pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(a)\r\nWhere the proper officer is satisfied, for reasons to be recorded in writing,\r\nthat there are sufficient grounds for revocation of cancellation of\r\nregistration, he shall revoke the cancellation of registration by an order in <b>FORM\r\nGST REG-22</b> within a period of thirty days from the date of the receipt of\r\nthe application and communicate the same to the applicant.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.55pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:21.95pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:71.9pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The proper officer may, for reasons to be\r\nrecorded in writing, under circumstances other than those specified in clause\r\n(a), by an order in <b>FORM GST</b> <b>REG-05</b>, reject the application for\r\nrevocation of cancellation of registration and<b> </b>communicate the same to\r\nthe applicant.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.55pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:.1pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:35.9pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: 