(48, 18, 'CGST Rule 24', 'Rule 24 : Migration of persons registered under the existing law', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">CHAPTER III -REGISTRATION<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:10.95pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-14.1pt;line-height:113%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">24.</span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Migration of persons\r\nregistered under the existinglaw.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-14.1pt;line-height:113%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><br></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1) (a) Every person, other<b> </b>than a\r\nperson deducting tax at source or an Input Service Distributor, registered\r\nunder an existing law and having a Permanent Account Number issued under the\r\nprovisions of the Income-tax Act, 1961 (Act 43 of 1961) shall enrol on the\r\ncommon portal by validating his e-mail address and mobile number, either\r\ndirectly or through a Facilitation Centre notified by the Commissioner.<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.65pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:28.55pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:59.45pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Upon\r\nenrolment under clause (a), the said person shall be granted registration on a\r\nprovisional basis and a certificate of registration in<b>FORM GST REG-25</b>,\r\nincorporating the Goods and Services Tax Identification Number therein, shall\r\nbe made available to him on the common portal:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.55pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:28.45pt;line-height:113%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that a taxable person who has been\r\ngranted multiple registrations under the existing law on the basis of a single\r\nPermanent Account Number shall be granted only one provisional registration\r\nunder the Act:</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:113%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)(a) Every person who has been granted a\r\nprovisional registration under sub-rule (1) shall submit an application\r\nelectronically in <b>FORM GST REG–26</b>, duly signed or verified through\r\nelectronic verification code, along with the information and documents\r\nspecified in the said application, on the common portal either directly or\r\nthrough a Facilitation Centre notified by the Commissioner.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.55pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:28.55pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:60.3pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The information asked for in clause (a)\r\nshall be furnished within a period of three months or within such further\r\nperiod as may be extended by the Commissioner in this behalf.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:28.55pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:59.6pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(c)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">If the\r\ninformation and the particulars furnished in the application are found, by the\r\nproper officer, to be correct and complete, a certificate of registration in <b>FORM</b>\r\n<b>GST REG-06 </b>shall be made available to the registered person\r\nelectronically on the<b> </b>common portal.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.55pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(3)Where the particulars or information\r\nspecified in sub-rule (2) have either not been furnished or not found to be\r\ncorrect orcomplete, the proper officer shall, after serving a notice to show\r\ncause in <b>FORM GST REG-27</b> and after affording the person concerned a\r\nreasonable opportunity of being heard, cancel the provisional registration\r\ngranted under sub-rule (1) and issue an order in <b>FORM GST REG-28</b>:</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.55pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[(3A) Where a certificate of registration has not been made\r\navailable to the applicant on the common portal within a period of fifteen days\r\nfrom the date of the furnishing of information and particulars referred to in\r\nclause (c) of sub-rule (2) and no notice has been issued under sub-rule (3)\r\nwithin the said period, the registration shall be deemed to have been granted\r\nand the said certificate of registration, duly signed or verified through\r\nelectronic verification code, shall be made available to the registered person\r\non the common portal.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.75pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:28.45pt;line-height:110%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that the show cause notice issued\r\nin<b>FORM GST REG- 27</b> can be withdrawn by issuing an order in<b>FORM GST\r\nREG- 20</b>, if it is found, after affording</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:110%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:13.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:122%\"><a name=\"page23\"></a><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n122%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">the person an opportunity of being heard,\r\nthat no such cause exists for which the notice was issued.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:122%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">32</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:122%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:1.75pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">(4)Every person registered\r\nunder any of the existing laws, who is not liable to be registered under the\r\nAct may, on or before [31</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">st</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">March,\r\n2018]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">33</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">34</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">,at his option, submit an\r\napplication electronically in <b>FORM GST REG-29</b> at the common portal for\r\nthe cancellation of registration granted to him and the proper officer shall,\r\nafter conducting such enquiry as deemed fit, cancel the said registration</span><br></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iii_registration_rule_24', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:16:33', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:16:33'),
(49, 18, 'CGST Rule 25', 'Rule 25 : Physical verification of business premises in certain cases', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;CHAPTER III- REGISTRATION<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:7.35pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.1pt;line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">25</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[</span><a href=\"file:///E:/Sidd%20-%20Backup/Important/SIDD%20GST/Return%20Paper%20on%20new%20model/Return%20Model%20after%20LC%20September%202018/SIDD%20GST/Rules%20Updated%202019/28.06.2019_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx%23ToC\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Physical\r\nverification of business premises in certain cases.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.1pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Where\r\nthe proper officer<b> </b>is satisfied that the physical verification of the\r\nplace of business of a person is required due to failure of Aadhaar\r\nauthentication before the grant of registration, or due to any other reason\r\nafter the grant of registration, he may get such verification of the place of\r\nbusiness, in the presence of the said person, done and the verification report\r\nalong with the other documents, including photographs, shall be uploaded in\r\nFORM GST REG-30 on the common portal within a period of fifteen working days\r\nfollowing the date of such verification.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">35<o:p></o:p></span></sup></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iii_registration_rule_25', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:16:12', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:16:12');
