(50, 18, 'CGST Rule 26', 'Rule 26 : Method of authentication', '<div class=\"WordSection1\">\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;CHAPTER III -REGISTRATION<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:7.2pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><b style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -14.1pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">26.</span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -14.1pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 0.875rem;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Method\r\nof authentication.</span></b></a><b style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -14.1pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.1pt;line-height:113%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)All applications, including reply, if\r\nany, to the notices,<b> </b>returns including the details of outward and inward\r\nsupplies, appeals or any other document required to be submitted under the\r\nprovisions of these rules shall be so submitted electronically with digital\r\nsignature certificate or through e-signature as specified under the provisions\r\nof the Information Technology Act, 2000 (21 of 2000) or verified by any other\r\nmode of signature or verification as notified by the Board in this behalf:<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.4pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:14.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:28.45pt;line-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that a registered person registered\r\nunder the provisions of the Companies Act, 2013 (18 of 2013) shall furnish the\r\ndocuments or application verified through digital signature certificate.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.35pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:39.0pt;line-height:105%\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[Provided further that a\r\nregistered person registered under the provisions of the Companies Act, 2013\r\n(18 of 2013) shall, during the period from the 21</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">st</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> day of\r\nApril, 2020 to the 30</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">th</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> day of September, 2020, also be allowed to\r\nfurnish the return under section 39 in <b>FORM GSTR-3B</b> verified through\r\nelectronic verification code (EVC).</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:1.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:36.0pt;line-height:110%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided also that a registered person\r\nregistered under the provisions of the Companies Act, 2013 (18 of 2013) shall,\r\nduring the period from the 27</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">th</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> day of May, 2020 to the 30</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">th</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> day of\r\nSeptember, 2020, also be allowed to furnish the details of outward supplies\r\nunder section 37 in <b>FORM GSTR-1</b> verified through electronic verification\r\ncode (EVC). ]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:110%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">36</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:110%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:1.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:line\r\n id=\"Shape_x0020_19\" o:spid=\"_x0000_s1027\" style=\'position:absolute;z-index:-251729408;\r\n visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square;mso-wrap-distance-left:9pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-top:0;mso-wrap-distance-right:9pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distan