listo MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(d)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">if the\r\nvalue is not determinable under clause (a) or clause (b) or clause (c), be the\r\nsum total of consideration in money and such further amount in money that is\r\nequivalent to consideration not in money as determined by the application of\r\nrule 30 or rule 31 in that order.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.05pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:14.05pt\"><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Illustration:</span></i><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:8.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:28.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:.25pt;line-height:112%;mso-list:l0 level3 lfo2;tab-stops:44.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span></i><!--[endif]--><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Where a\r\nnew phone is supplied for twenty thousand rupees along with the exchange of an\r\nold phone and if the price of the new phone without exchange is twenty four\r\nthousand rupees, the open market value of the new phone is twenty four thousand\r\nrupees.<o:p></o:p></span></i></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.9pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></i></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:28.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:.25pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l0 level3 lfo2;tab-stops:43.75pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span></i><!--[endif]--><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Where a\r\nlaptop is supplied for forty thousand rupees along with the barter of a printer\r\nthat is manufactured by the recipient and the value of the printer known at the\r\ntime of supply is four thousand rupees but the open market value of the laptop\r\nis not known, the value of the supply of the laptop is forty four thousand\r\nrupees.<o:p></o:p></span></i></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></i></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></i></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iv_determination_of_value_of_supply_rule_27', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:00:09', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:00:09');
