(52, 18, 'CGST Rule 28', 'Rule 28 : Value of supply of goods or services or both between distinct or related persons, other than through an agent', '<h6 style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: 5.3pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST)\r\nRules, 2017</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">CHAPTER IV - DETERMINATION OF VALUE OF SUPPLY</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></h6><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:103.05pt\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.05pt;line-height:109%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:20.6pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:109%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">28.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 109%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Value of supply of goods or services or both between\r\ndistinct or related persons,</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:109%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> </span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 109%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">other than through\r\nan agent.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:109%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.05pt;line-height:109%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:20.6pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:109%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><br></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:109%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The value of the supply of goods or services\r\nor both<b> </b>between distinct persons as specified in sub-section (4) and (5)\r\nof section 25 or where the supplier and recipient are related, other than where\r\nthe supply is made through an agent, shall-<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.95pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.05pt;text-indent:-36.2pt;mso-list:\r\nl0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:54.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">(a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">be the\r\nopen market value of such supply;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.35pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:54.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-36.2pt;line-height:112%;\r\nmso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:54.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">(b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">if the open market value is not available,\r\nbe the value of supply of goods or services of like kind and quality;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.75pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:54.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-36.2pt;line-height:111%;\r\nmso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:54.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:111%;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">(c)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:111%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">if the value is not determinable under\r\nclause (a) or (b), be the value as determined by the application of rule 30 or\r\nrule 31, in that order:</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:111%;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.75pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that where the goods\r\nare intended for further supply as such by the recipient, the value shall, at\r\nthe option of the supplier, be an amount equivalent to ninety percent of the\r\nprice charged for the supply of goods of like kind and quality by the recipient\r\nto his customer not being a related person:</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:36.0pt;line-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided further that where the recipient is\r\neligible for full input tax credit, the value declared in the invoice shall be\r\ndeemed to be the open market value of the goods or services.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iv_determination_of_value_of_supply_rule_28', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:00:43', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:00:43'),
(53, 18, 'CGST Rule 29', 'Rule 29 : Value of supply of goods made or received through an agent', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:11.05pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST)\r\nRules, 2017</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:\r\ncenter\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">CHAPTER IV - DETERMINATION OF VALUE OF SUPPLY</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.75pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:107%;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:24.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">29.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Value of supply of goods made or received through an\r\nagent.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:107%;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:24.05pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><br></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The value of supply<b> </b>of goods between\r\nthe principal and his agent shall-<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:7.25pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:14.1pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:36.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">be the open market value of the goods being\r\nsupplied, or at the option of the supplier, be ninety percent. of the price\r\ncharged for the supply of goods of like kind and quality by the recipient to\r\nhis customer not being a related person, where the goods are intended for\r\nfurther supply by the said recipient.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:114%\"><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Illustration: A principal supplies groundnut to his agent and the\r\nagent is supplying groundnuts of like kind and quality in subsequent supplies\r\nat a price of five thousand rupees per quintal on the day of the supply.\r\nAnother independent supplier is supplying groundnuts of like kind and quality\r\nto the said agent at the price of four thousand five hundred and fifty rupees\r\nper quintal. The value of the supply made by the principal shall be four\r\nthousand five hundred and fifty rupees per quintal or where he exercises the\r\noption, the value shall be 90 per cent. of five thousand rupees i.e., four\r\nthousand five hundred rupees per quintal.</span></i><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.85pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">where the value of a supply\r\nis not determinable under clause (a), the same shall be determined by the\r\napplication of rule 30 or rule 31 in that order</span><br></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iv_determination_of_value_of_supply_rule_29', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:01:22', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:01:22'),
(54, 18, 'CGST Rule 30', 'Rule 30 : Value of supply of goods or services or both based on cost', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:11.05pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST)\r\nRules, 2017</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:\r\ncenter\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">CHAPTER IV - DETERMINATION OF VALUE OF SUPPLY</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.05pt;line-height:112%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:20.7pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">30.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Value of supply of goods or services or both based on\r\ncost.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.05pt;line-height:112%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:20.7pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><br></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Where the value of a<b> </b>supply of goods\r\nor services or both is not determinable by any of the preceding rules of this\r\nChapter, the value shall be one hundred and ten percent of the cost of\r\nproduction or manufacture or the cost of acquisition of such goods or the cost\r\nof provision of such services.<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iv_determination_of_value_of_supply_rule_30', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:02:02', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:02:02'),
(55, 18, 'CGST Rule 31', 'Rule 31 : Residual method for determination of value of supply of goods or services or both', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:11.05pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST)\r\nRules, 2017</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:\r\ncenter\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">CHAPTER IV - DETERMINATION OF VALUE OF SUPPLY</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:11.1pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:107%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">31.</span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Residual method for\r\ndetermination of value of supply of goods or services or both.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:107%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><br></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Where\r\nthe value of supply of goods or services or both cannot be determined under\r\nrules 27 to 30, the same shall be determined using reasonable means consistent\r\nwith the principles and the general provisions of section 15 and the provisions\r\nof this Chapter:<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:7.35pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:36.0pt;line-height:113%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that in the case of supply of\r\nservices, the supplier may opt for this rule, ignoring rule 30.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:113%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iv_determination_of_value_of_supply_rule_31', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:02:35', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:02:35'),
(56, 18, 'CGST Rule 31A', 'Rule 31A : Value of supply in case of lottery, betting, gambling and horse racing.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:11.05pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST)\r\nRules, 2017</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:\r\ncenter\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">CHAPTER IV - DETERMINATION OF VALUE OF SUPPLY</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[31A. </span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Value of supply in case of lottery, betting, gambling\r\nand horse racing. </span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.4pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">Notwithstanding\r\nanything contained in the provisions of this Chapter, the value in respect of\r\nsupplies specified below shall be determined in the manner provided\r\nhereinafter.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:8.85pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">[(2)\r\nThe value of supply of lottery shall be deemed to be 100/128 of the face value\r\nof ticket or of the price as notified in the Official Gazette by the Organising\r\nState, whichever is higher.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:138%\"><a name=\"page27\"></a><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:138%;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Explanation</span></i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:138%;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">:–<i>\r\n</i>For the purposes of this sub-rule, the expression<i> </i>?Organising State?<i>\r\n</i>has<i> </i>the same meaning as assigned to it in clause (f) of sub-rule (1)\r\nof rule 2 of the Lotteries (Regulation) Rules, 2010.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:138%;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">38</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:138%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 118%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 118%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">The value of supply of actionable claim in\r\nthe form of chance to win in betting, gambling or horse racing in a race club\r\nshall be 100% of the face value of the bet or the amount paid into the\r\ntotalisator.]</span><sup style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.05pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:118%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">39</span></sup></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:15.05pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iv_determination_of_value_of_supply_rule_31a', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:03:02', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:03:02');
