(57, 18, 'CGST Rule 32', 'Rule 32 : Determination of value in respect of certain supplies', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:11.05pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST)\r\nRules, 2017</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:\r\ncenter\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">CHAPTER IV - DETERMINATION OF VALUE OF SUPPLY</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:15.05pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:112%;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:20.1pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">32.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Determination\r\nof value in respect of certain supplies.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:112%;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:20.1pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)Notwithstanding\r\nanything<b> </b>contained in the provisions of this Chapter, the value in\r\nrespect of supplies specified below shall, at the option of the supplier, be\r\ndetermined in the manner provided hereinafter.<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.85pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.05pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:17.45pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The value of supply of services in relation\r\nto the purchase or sale of foreign currency, including money changing, shall be\r\ndetermined by the supplier of services in the following manner, namely:-<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.3pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:36.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.05pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l11 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:53.35pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">for a currency, when exchanged from, or to,\r\nIndian Rupees, the value shall be equal to the difference in the buying rate or\r\nthe selling rate, as the case may be, and the Reserve Bank of India reference\r\nrate for that currency at that time, multiplied by the total units of currency:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.25pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:36.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:63.25pt;line-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that in case where the Reserve Bank\r\nof India reference rate for a currency is not available, the value shall be one\r\nper cent. of the gross amount of Indian Rupees provided or received by the\r\nperson changing the money:</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:\r\n114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:63.25pt;line-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided further that in case\r\nwhere neither of the currencies exchanged is Indian Rupees, the value shall be\r\nequal to one per cent. of the lesser of the two amounts the person changing the\r\nmoney would have received by converting any of the two currencies into Indian\r\nRupee on that day at the reference rate provided by the Reserve Bank of India.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 63.25pt;\">Provided also that a person supplying the\r\nservices may exercise the option to ascertain the value in terms of clause (b)\r\nfor a financial year and such option shall not be withdrawn during the\r\nremaining part of that financial year.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:6.3pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"fo