tified by the Government, on the\r\nrecommendations of the Council, as referred to in paragraph 2 of Schedule I of\r\nthe said Act between distinct persons as referred to in section 25, where input\r\ntax credit is available, shall be deemed to be NIL.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.55pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iv_determination_of_value_of_supply_rule_32', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:03:32', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:03:32'),
