l, 2019 shall be deemed to be the value determined in terms of\r\nsection 15 of the Act, but shall not include the said cess.]</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; margin-right: 5.3pt; text-align: center; line-height: 14.7px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:11.05pt\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: center;\"><br></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_iv_determination_of_value_of_supply_rule_32a', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:06:21', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 15:06:21');
