(59, 18, 'CGST Rule 33', 'Rule 33 : Value of supply of services in case of pure agent', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:11.05pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST)\r\nRules, 2017</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:\r\ncenter\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">CHAPTER IV - DETERMINATION OF VALUE OF SUPPLY</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:112%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">33.</span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Value of supply of services in case of pure agent.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:112%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><br></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Notwithstanding\r\nanything<b> </b>contained in the provisions of this Chapter, the expenditure or\r\ncosts incurred by a supplier as a pure agent of the recipient of supply shall\r\nbe excluded from the value of supply, if all the following conditions are\r\nsatisfied, namely,-<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.85pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:36.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:113%;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:50.95pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(i)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">the supplier acts as a pure agent of the\r\nrecipient of the supply, when he makes the payment to the third party on\r\nauthorisation by such recipient;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.4pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:54.75pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(ii)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">the\r\npayment made by the pure agent on behalf of the recipient of supply has been\r\nseparately indicated in the invoice issued by the pure agent to the recipient\r\nof service; and<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.4pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:36.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:57.15pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(iii)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">the\r\nsupplies procured by the pure agent from the third party as a pure agent of the\r\nrecipient of supply are in addition to the services he supplies on his own\r\naccount.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:109%\"><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:109%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Explanation<b>.</b>-\r\n</span></i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:109%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Arial\">For the purposes of this rule, the expression\r\n?pure agent? means a person</span><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n109%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> </span></i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:109%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">who-</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:109%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:1.05pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:36.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:54.15pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">enters into a contractual agreement with the\r\nrecipient of supply to act as his pure agent to incur expenditure or costs in\r\nthe course of supply of goods or services or both;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:36.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:113%;\r\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:54.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">neither intends to hold nor holds any title\r\nto the goods or services or both so procured or supplied as pure agent of the\r\nrecipient of supply;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.25pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:52.05pt;text-indent:-16.05pt;mso-list:\r\nl1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:52.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(c)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">does not use for his own\r\ninterest such goods or services so procured; and<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.2pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:36.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:113%;\r\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:54.3pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(d)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">receives only the actual amount incurred to\r\nprocure such goods or services in addition to the amount received for supply he\r\nprovides on his own account.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.35pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:113%\"><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Illustration</span></i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">.<i>- </i>Corporate services firm A is\r\nengaged to handle the legal work pertaining to<i> </i>the incorporation of\r\nCompany B. Other than its service fees, A also recovers from B, registration\r\nfee and approval fee for the name of the company paid to the Registrar of\r\nCompanies. The fees charged by the Registrar of Companies for the registration\r\nand approval of the name are compulsorily levied on B. A is merely acting as a\r\npure agent in </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial\">the payment of those fees.\r\nTherefore, A‘s recovery of such expenses is a disbursement and </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">not\r\npart of the value of supply made by A to B.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:1.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:line\r\n id=\"Shape_x0020_22\" o:spid=\"_x0000_s1026\" style=\'position:absolute;z-index:-251726336;\r\n visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square;mso-wrap-distance-left:9pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-top:0;mso-wrap-distance-right:9pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-bottom:0;mso-position-horizontal:absolute;\r\n mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;mso-position-vertical:absolute;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:text\' from=\"0,33.95pt\" to=\"2in,33.95pt\"\r\n o:gfxdata=\"UEsDBBQABgAIAAAAIQC75UiUBQEAAB4CAAATAAAAW0NvbnRlbnRfVHlwZXNdLnhtbKSRvU7DMBSF\r\ndyTewfKKEqcMCKEmHfgZgaE8wMW+SSwc27JvS/v23KTJgkoXFsu+P+c7Ol5vDoMTe0zZBl/LVVlJ\r\ngV4HY31Xy4/tS3EvRSbwBlzwWMsjZrlprq/W22PELHjb51r2RPFBqax7HCCXIaLnThvSAMTP1KkI\r\n+gs6VLdVdad08ISeCho1ZLN+whZ2jsTzgcsnJwldluLxNDiyagkxOquB2Knae/OLUsyEkjenmdzb\r\nmG/YhlRnCWPnb8C898bRJGtQvEOiVxjYhtLOxs8AySiT4JuDystlVV4WPeM6tK3VaILeDZxIOSsu\r\nti/jidNGNZ3/J08yC1dNv9v8AAAA//8DAFBLAwQUAAYACAAAACEArTA/8cEAAAAyAQAACwAAAF9y\r\nZWxzLy5yZWxzhI/NCsIwEITvgu8Q9m7TehCRpr2I4FX0AdZk2wbbJGTj39ubi6AgeJtl2G9m6vYx\r\njeJGka13CqqiBEFOe2Ndr+B03C3WIDihMzh6RwqexNA281l9oBFTfuLBBhaZ4ljBkFLYSMl6oAm5\r\n8IFcdjofJ0z5jL0MqC/Yk1yW5UrGTwY0X0yxNwri3lQgjs+Qk/+zfddZTVuvrxO59