rritory</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> </span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">tax.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.05pt;line-height:107%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:20.2pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><br></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Where\r\nthe value of supply is inclusive of integrated tax or, as the case may be,<b> </b>central\r\ntax, State tax, Union territory tax, the tax amount shall be determined in the\r\nfollowing manner, namely,-<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:17.3pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tax\r\namount = (Value inclusive of taxes X tax rate in % of IGST or, as the case may\r\nbe, CGST, SGST or UTGST) ÷ (100+ sum of tax rates, as applicable, in %)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.1pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Explanation.-</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">For the purposes of the\r\nprovisions of this Chapter, the expressions-</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:8.7pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b><b style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -3.05pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -3.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">?open market value? of a supply of goods or\r\nservices or both means the full </span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -3.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">value</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -3.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -3.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">in\r\nmoney, excluding the integrated tax, central tax, State tax, Union territory\r\ntax and the cess payable by a person in a transaction, where the supplier and\r\nthe recipient of the supply are not related and the price is the sole\r\nconsideration, to obtain such supply at the same time when the supply being\r\nvalued is made;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:7.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:21.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-3.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:35.7pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n113%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial\">?supply of\r\ngoods or services or both of like kind and quality? means any other </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">supply\r\nof goods or services or both made under similar circumstances that, in respect\r\nof the characteristics, quality, quantity, functional components, materials,\r\nand the reputation of the goods or services or both first mentioned, is the\r\nsame as, or closely or substantially resembles, that supply of goods or\r\nservices or both.<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:1.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:line\r\n id=\"Shape_x0020_23\" o:spid=\"_x0000_s1026\" style=\'position:absolute;z-index:-251725312;\r\n visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square;mso-wrap-distance-left:9pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-top:0;mso-wrap-distance-right:9pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-bottom:0;mso-position-horizontal:absolute;\r\n mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;mso-position-vertical:absolute;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:text\' from=\"0,171.85pt\" to=\"2in,171.85pt\"\r\n o:gfxdata=\"UEsDBBQABgAIAAAAIQC75UiUBQEAAB4CAAATAAAAW0NvbnRlbnRfVHlwZXNdLnhtbKSRvU7DMBSF\r\ndyTewfKKEqcMCKEmHfgZgaE8wMW+SSwc27JvS/v23KTJgkoXFsu+P+c7Ol5vDoMTe0zZBl/LVVlJ\r\ngV4HY31Xy4/tS3EvRSbwBlzwWMsjZrlprq/W22PELHjb51r2RPFBqax7HCCXIaLnThvSAMTP1KkI\r\n+gs6VLdVdad08ISeCho1ZLN+whZ2jsTzgcsnJwldluLxNDiyagkxOquB2Knae/OLUsyEkjenmdzb\r\nmG/YhlRnCWPnb8C898bRJGtQvEOiVxjYhtLOxs8AySiT4JuDystlVV4WPeM6tK3VaILeDZxIOSsu\r\nti/jidNGNZ3/J08yC1dNv9v8AAAA//8DAFBLAwQUAAYACAAAACEArTA/8cEAAAAyAQAACwAAAF9y\r\nZWxzLy5yZWxzhI/NCsIwEITvgu8Q9m7TehCRpr2I4FX0AdZk2wbbJGTj39ubi6AgeJtl2G9m6vYx\r\njeJGka13CqqiBEFOe2Ndr+B03C3WIDihMzh6RwqexNA281l9oBFTfuLBBhaZ4ljBkFLYSMl6oAm5\r\n8IFcdjofJ0z5jL0MqC/Yk1yW5UrGTwY0X0yxNwri3lQgjs+Qk/+zfddZTVuvrxO59CNCmoj3vCwj\r\nMfaUFOjRhrPHaN4Wv0VV5OYgm1p+LW1eAAAA//8DAFBLAwQUAAYACAAAACEAXfHsiK8BAADXAwAA\r\nHwAAAGNsaXBib2FyZC9kcmF3aW5ncy9kcmF3aW5nMS54bWykU01vozAQvVfa/2D5vgWy3Yigkh6y\r\nTS9VWyntD5gaB6z6A9leSv99