(62, 18, 'CGST Rule 36', 'Rule 36 : Documentary requirements and conditions for claiming input tax credit', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST)\r\nRules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;CHAPTER V -INPUT TAX CREDIT<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:57.05pt;text-indent:-57.05pt;mso-list:\r\nl0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:57.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">36.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Documentary requirements and conditions for claiming input\r\ntax credit.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.35pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:113%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)The\r\ninput tax credit shall be availed by a registered person, including the Input\r\nService Distributor, on the basis of any of the following documents, namely,-<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:57.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-28.75pt;line-height:\r\n113%;mso-list:l0 level3 lfo1;tab-stops:57.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">an invoice issued by the supplier of goods\r\nor services or both in accordance with the provisions of section 31;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.25pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-indent: -28.75pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -28.75pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">an\r\ninvoice issued in accordance with the provisions of clause (f) of sub-section</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.1pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt;\">(3) of section 31, subject to the payment of\r\ntax;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.2pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-indent: -28.75pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(c)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -28.75pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">a debit note issued by a supplier in\r\naccordance with the provisions of section 34;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -28.75pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(d)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -28.75pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">a bill of entry or any similar document\r\nprescribed under the Customs Act, 1962 or rules made thereunder for the\r\nassessment of integrated tax on imports;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.4pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -28.75pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(e)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -28.75pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">an Input Service Distributor invoice or\r\nInput Service Distributor credit note or any document issued by an Input\r\nService Distributor in accordance with the provisions of sub-rule (1) of rule 54.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:0cm;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Input tax credit shall be availed by a\r\nregistered person only if all the applicable particulars as specified in the\r\nprovisions of Chapter VI are contained in the said document, and the relevant\r\ninformation, as contained in the said document, is furnished in <b>FORMGSTR-2</b>bysuch\r\nperson:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:117%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:117%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[Provided that if the said document does not contain all the\r\nspecified particulars but contains the details of the amount of tax charged,\r\ndescription of goods or services, total value of supply of goods or services or\r\nboth, GSTIN of the supplier and recipient and place of supply in case of\r\ninter-State supply, input tax credit may be availed by such registered person.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:117%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">42</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:117%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:0cm;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">No input tax credit shall be availed by a\r\nregistered person in respect of any tax that has been paid in pursuance of any\r\norder where any demand has been confirmed on account of any fraud, willful\r\nmisstatement or suppression of facts.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:7.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:113%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[(4) Input tax credit to be availed by a\r\nregistered person in respect of invoices or debit notes, the details of which\r\nhave not been uploaded by the suppliers under sub-section (1) of section 37,\r\nshall not exceed [10 per cent]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">43</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">of the eligible credit available in respect\r\nof invoices or debit notes the details of which have been uploaded by the\r\nsuppliers under sub-section (1) of section 37.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">44</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:113%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:1.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:line\r\n id=\"Shape_x0020_24\" o:spid=\"_x0000_s1026\" style=\'position:absolute;z-index:-251724288;\r\n visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square;mso-wrap-distance-left:9pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-top:0;