(63, 18, 'CGST Rule 37', 'Rule 37 : Reversal of input tax credit in the case of non-payment of consideration', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST)\r\nRules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;CHAPTER V- INPUT TAX CREDIT<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.8pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:21.8pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">37.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Reversal\r\nof input tax credit in the case of non-payment of consideration.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:21.8pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)A<b>\r\n</b>registered person, who has availed of input tax credit on any inward supply\r\nof goods or services or both, but fails to pay to the supplier thereof, the\r\nvalue of such supply along with the tax payable thereon, within the time limit\r\nspecified in the second proviso to sub-section(2) of section 16, shall furnish\r\nthe details of such supply, the amount of value not paid and the amount of\r\ninput tax credit availed of proportionate to such amount not paid to the\r\nsupplier in <b>FORM GSTR-2</b> for the month immediately following the period\r\nof one hundred and eighty days from the date of the issue of the invoice:<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.7pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:113%\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that the value of\r\nsupplies made without consideration as specified in Schedule I of the said Act\r\nshall be deemed to have been paid for the purposes of the second proviso to\r\nsub-section (2) of section 16:<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:117%\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:117%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[Provided further that the\r\nvalue of supplies on account of any amount added in accordance with the\r\nprovisions of clause (b) of sub-section (2) of section 15 shall be deemed to\r\nhave been paid for the purposes of the second proviso to sub-section (2) of\r\nsection 16.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:117%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">46</span></sup><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:117%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:12.55pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">The amountof input tax credit referred to in\r\nsub-rule (1) shall be added to the output tax liability of the registered\r\nperson for the month in which the details are furnished.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.35pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">The\r\nregistered person shall be liable to pay interest at the rate notified under sub-section\r\n(1) of section 50 for the period startingfrom the date of availing credit on\r\nsuch supplies tillthe date when the amount added to the output tax liability,\r\nas mentioned in sub-rule (2), is paid.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.4pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt;\">The time limit specified in\r\nsub-section (4) of section 16 shall not apply to a claim for re-availing of any\r\ncredit, in accordance with the provisions of the Act or the provisions of this\r\nChapter,that had been reversed earlier</span></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_v__input_tax_credit_rule_37', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:35:07', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:35:07'),
