(65, 18, 'CGST Rule 39', 'Rule 39 : Procedure for distribution of input tax credit by Input Service Distributor', '<div class=\"WordSection1\">\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">CHAPTER V -INPUT TAX CREDIT<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:111%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:29.95pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:111%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">39.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 111%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Procedure for distribution of input tax credit by\r\nInput Service Distributor.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:111%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:111%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:29.95pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:111%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)An<b> </b>Input Service Distributor shall\r\ndistribute input tax credit in the manner and subject to the following\r\nconditions, namely,-<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.7pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</o:p></span></b><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -36.15pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -36.15pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">the input tax credit available for\r\ndistribution in a month shall be distributed in the same month and the&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;details\r\nthereof shall be furnishedin<b>FORM</b> <b>GSTR-6</b>in accordance with the\r\nprovisions of Chapter VIII of&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;these&nbsp; rules;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.3pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -36.15pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -36.15pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">the Input Service Distributor shall, in\r\naccordance with the provisions of clause (d), separately distribute the&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;amount\r\nof ineligible input tax credit (ineligible under the provisions of sub-section\r\n(5) of section 17 or&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;otherwise) and the amount of eligible input tax credit;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.4pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -36.15pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(c)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -36.15pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">the input tax credit on account of central\r\ntax, State tax, Union territory tax and integrated tax shall be&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; distributed\r\nseparately in accordance with the provisions of clause (d);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -36.15pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(d)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -36.15pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">the input tax credit that is required to be\r\ndistributed in accordance with the provisions of clause (d) and (e)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;of\r\nsub-section (2) of section 20 to one of the </span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -36.15pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">recipients\r\n?R1‘, whether registered or not, from amongst the&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;total of all the </span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -36.15pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">recipients\r\nto whom input tax credit is attributable, including the recipient(s) who are\r\nengaged&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; in making exempt supply, or are otherwise not registered </span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -36.15pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">for any reason, shall be the amount, ?C1?, to&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;be&nbsp; calculated by applying the </span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -36.15pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">following formula -</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:14.95pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</o:p></span><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">C</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><sub><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">1</span></sub></b><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> = (t</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><sub><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">1</span></sub></b><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">÷T) × C</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.05pt\"><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;where,</span></i><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:2.15pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</o:p></span><i style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">“C” is the amount of credit to be\r\ndistributed,</span></i></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:4.3pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</o:p></span><i style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:119%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;“t</span></i><i style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><sub><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:119%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">1</span></sub></i><i style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:119%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">” is\r\nthe turnover</span></i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 119%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">, as referred to in section 20,<i> of person\r\nR</i></span><i style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><sub><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:119%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">1</span></sub></i><i style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n119%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> during the relevant period, and</span></i></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.1pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </o:p></span><i style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">“T” is\r\nthe aggregate of the turnover, during the relevant period, of all recipients to\r\nwhom the input service is attributable&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;in accordance with the provisions of\r\nsection 20;</span></i></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:12.95pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-indent: -27.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(e)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -27.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">the input tax credit on account of\r\nintegrated tax shall be distributed as input tax credit of integrated tax to&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; every recipient;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:27.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:.25pt;line-height:112%;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:50.85pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; (f)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">the input tax credit on account of central\r\ntax and State tax or Union territory tax shall-<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.6pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:63.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.2pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo3;tab-stops:78.85pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(i)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">in respect of a recipient located in the\r\nsame State or Union territory in which the Input Service&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Distributor is\r\nlocated, be distributed as input tax credit of central tax and State tax or\r\nUnion territory&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; tax respectively;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.3pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.2pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; (ii)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.2pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">in\r\nrespect of a recipient located in a State or Union territory other than that of\r\nthe Input Service&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Distributor, be distributed as integrated tax and the amount\r\nto be so distributed shall be equal to the&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; aggregate of the amount of input tax\r\ncredit of central tax and State tax or Union territory tax that&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; qualifies for\r\ndistribution to such recipient in accordance with clause (d);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.55pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.25pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(g)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.25pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">the Input Service Distributor shall issue an\r\nInput Service Distributor invoice, as prescribed in sub-rule (1) of&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; rule 54,\r\nclearly indicating in such invoice that it is issued only for distribution of\r\ninput tax credit;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:27.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:.25pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:44.75pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp; (h)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">the Input Service Distributor shall issue an\r\nInput Service Distributor credit note, as prescribed in sub-rule (1)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;of rule\r\n54, for reduction of credit in case the input tax credit already distributed\r\ngets reduced for any reason;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:27.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(i)any additional amount of input tax credit on account of\r\nissuance of a debit note to an Input Service Distributor by the supplier shall\r\nbe distributed in the manner and subject to the conditions specified in clauses\r\n(a) to (f) and the amount attributable to any recipient shall be calculated in\r\nthe manner provided in clause (d) and such credit shall be distributed in the\r\nmonth in which the debit note isincluded in the return in <b>FORM GSTR-6;</b></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.6pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:26.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:1.25pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo4;\r\ntab-stops:41.25pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(j)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">any\r\ninput tax credit required to be reduced on account of issuance of a credit note\r\nto the Input Service Distributor by the supplier shall be apportioned to each\r\nrecipient in the same ratio in which the input tax credit contained in the\r\noriginal invoice was distributed in terms of clause (d), and the amount so\r\napportioned shall be-<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div><p>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -14.4pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(i)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -14.4pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">reduced\r\nfrom the amount to be note is included in the return in</span></p><div class=\"WordSection2\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:1.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 0.2pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;distributed\r\nin the month in which the credit </span><b style=\"font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 0.2pt;\">FORM GSTR-6</b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 0.2pt;\">; or</span><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:1.0pt;text-indent:.2pt;line-height:112%\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n</div><p>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><br clear=\"all\" style=\"page-break-before:always;mso-break-type:section-break\">\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:57.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.4pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo6;tab-stops:77.1pt\"><a name=\"page35\"></a><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(ii)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">added\r\nto the output tax liability of the recipient where the amount so apportioned is\r\nin the negative by virtue of the amount of credit under distribution being less\r\nthan the amount to be adjusted.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.45pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:113%;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo7;\r\ntab-stops:20.1pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">If the\r\namount of input tax credit distributed by an Input Service Distributor is\r\nreduced later on for any other reason for any of the recipients, including that\r\nit was distributed to a wrong recipient by the Input Service Distributor, the\r\nprocess specified in clause (j) of sub-rule (1) shall apply, <i>mutatis\r\nmutandis,</i> for reduction of credit.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.7pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo7;\r\ntab-stops:18.3pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Subject\r\nto sub-rule (2), the Input Service Distributor shall, on the basis of the Input\r\nService Distributor credit note specified in clause (h) of sub-rule (1), issue\r\nan Input Service Distributor invoice to the recipient entitled to such credit\r\nand include the Input Service Distributor credit note and the Input Service\r\nDistributor invoice in the return in <b>FORM</b> <b>GSTR-6 </b>for the month in\r\nwhich such credit note and invoice was issued.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_v__input_tax_credit_rule_39', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:36:12', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:36:12');
