(66, 18, 'CGST Rule 40', 'Rule 40 : Manner of claiming credit in special circumstances', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">&nbsp;CHAPTER V- INPUT TAX CREDIT<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.55pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:112%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:36.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">40.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 112%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Manner of claiming credit in special circumstances.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:112%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1) The\r\ninput tax credit<b> </b>claimed in accordance with the provisions of\r\nsub-section (1) of section 18 on the inputs held in stock or inputs contained\r\nin semi-finished or finished goods held in stock, or the credit claimed on\r\ncapital goods in accordance with the provisions of clauses (c) and (d) of the\r\nsaid sub-section, shall be subject to the following conditions, namely,-<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.6pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:54.4pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">the\r\ninput tax credit on capital goods, in terms of clauses (c) and (d) of\r\nsub-section (1) of section 18, shall be claimed after reducing the tax paid on\r\nsuch capital goods by five percentage points per quarter of a year or part\r\nthereof from the date of the invoice or such other documents on which the\r\ncapital goods were received by the taxable person.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.2pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[(b) the registered person shall within a\r\nperiod of thirty days from the date of becoming eligible to avail the input tax\r\ncredit under sub-section (1) of section 18, or within such further period as\r\nmay be extended by the Commissioner by a notification in this behalf, shall\r\nmake a declaration, electronically, on the common portal in <b>FORM GST ITC-01</b>\r\nto the effect that he is eligible to avail the input tax credit as aforesaid:</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:114%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.35pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:36.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:119%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:119%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that any ex