font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 114%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">The transferor shall also submit a copy of a\r\ncertificate issued by a practicing chartered accountant or cost accountant\r\ncertifying that the sale, merger, de-merger, amalgamation, lease or transfer of\r\nbusiness has been done with a specific provision for the transfer of\r\nliabilities.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.05pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:18.9pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The transferee shall, on the common portal,\r\naccept the details so furnished by the transferor and, upon such acceptance,\r\nthe un-utilized credit specified in <b>FORM GST</b> <b>ITC-02 </b>shall be\r\ncredited to his electronic credit ledger.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.3pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">(4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.05pt; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 113%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif;\">The inputs and capital goods so transferred\r\nshall be duly accounted for by the transferee in his books of account.</span></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_v__input_tax_credit_rule_41', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:37:37', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:37:37'),
(68, 18, 'CGST Rule 41A', 'Rule 41A : Transfer of credit on obtaining separate registration for multiple places of business within a State or Union territory', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">CHAPTER V- INPUT TAX CREDIT<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:111%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:111%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">[Rule 41A. Transfer of credit on obtaining separate registration\r\nfor multiple places of business within a State or Union territory.-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:111%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:111%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> </span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:111%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1) A\r\nregistered person who has obtained<b> </b>separate registration for multiple\r\nplaces of business in accordance with the provisions of rule 11 and who intends\r\nto transfer, either wholly or partly, the unutilised input tax credit lying in\r\nhis electronic credit ledger to any or all of the newly registered place of\r\nbusiness, shall furnish within a period of thirty days from obtaining such\r\nseparate registrations, the details in <b>FORM GST ITC-02A</b> electronically\r\non the common portal, either directly or through a Facilitation Centre notified\r\nin this behalf by the Commissioner:</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:111%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.9pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:36.0pt;line-height:113%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that the input tax credit shall be\r\ntransferred to the newly registered entities in the ratio of the value of\r\nassets held by them at the time of registration.</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.0pt;line-height:113%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.35pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:111%\"><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:111%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Explanation</span></i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n111%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">.- For the purposes of this sub-</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:111%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Arial\">rule, it is hereby clarified that the ?value of</span><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:111%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> </span></i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:111%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Arial\">assets‘ means the value of the entire assets of\r\nthe business whether or not input tax credit </span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:111%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">has been availed thereon.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:111%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:10.6pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:118%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:19.6pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:118%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:118%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The\r\nnewly registered person (transferee) shall, on the common portal, accept the\r\ndetails so furnished by the registered person (transferor) and, upon such\r\nacceptance, the unutilised input tax credit specified in <b>FORM GST ITC-02A</b>\r\nshall be credited to his electronic credit ledger.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:118%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">49</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:118%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'cgst_rule_2017_chapter_v__input_tax_credit_rule_41a', 0, 1, '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:38:08', '157.37.152.189', '2020-09-03 14:38:08');
