(73, 18, 'CGST Rule 45', 'Rule 45 : Conditions and restrictions in respect of inputs and capital goods sent to the job worker', '<div class=\"WordSection1\">\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right:5.3pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:105%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Central\r\nGoods and Services Tax (CGST) Rules, 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:105%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:15.75pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">CHAPTER V- INPUT TAX CREDIT</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.05pt;line-height:110%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:20.7pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">45.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">Conditions and restrictions in respect of inputs and\r\ncapital goods sent to the job</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> </span></b><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/DELL/Desktop/01.07.2020%20_CGST%20Rules,%202017_(Part-A_Rules).docx#page2\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: &quot;Calisto MT&quot;, serif; color: windowtext;\">worker.</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">-</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:-.05pt;line-height:110%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:20.7pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><br></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(1)The\r\ninputs, semi-finished goods or capital goods shall be sent to the job<b> </b>worker\r\nunder the cover of a challan issued by the principal, including where such\r\ngoods are sent directly to a job-worker, [and where the goods are sent from one\r\njob worker to another job worker, the challan may be issued either by the\r\nprincipal or the job worker sending the goods to another job worker:<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:1.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:114%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that the challan issued by the principal may be endorsed\r\nby the job worker, indicating therein the quantity and description of goods\r\nwhere the goods are sent by one job worker to another or are returned to the\r\nprincipal:<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.3pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:119%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:119%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided further that the challan endorsed by the job worker may\r\nbe further endorsed by another job worker, indicating therein the quantity and\r\ndescription of goods where the goods are sent by one job worker to another or\r\nare returned to the principal.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:119%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">79</span></sup><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:119%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:12.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:113%;\r\nmso-list:l3 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:17.1pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:113%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The challan issued by the principal to the\r\njob worker shall contain the details specified in rule 55.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.5pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:2.95pt;line-height:110%;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:20.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">The\r\ndetails of challans in respect of goods dispatched to a job worker or received\r\nfrom a job worker [<s>or sent from one job worker to another]</s></span><s><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">80</span></sup></s><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:110%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"> during\r\na quarter shall be included in <b>FORM GST ITC-04</b>furnished for that period\r\non or before the twenty-fifth day of the month succeeding the said quarter[or\r\nwithin such further period as may be extended by the Commissioner by a\r\nnotification in this behalf:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:.95pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:36.0pt;line-height:118%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n118%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">Provided that any extension of the time limit\r\nnotified by the Commissioner of State tax or the Commissioner of Union\r\nterritory tax shall be deemed to be notified by the Commissioner.]</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:118%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">81</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:118%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:12.3pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.05pt;line-height:114%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;\r\ntab-stops:18.8pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:114%;font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Calisto MT&quot;\">(4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:114%;fo